<br>
i got a new promotion about 6 weeks ago where i am working around 55-70 hours a week, all overnight shifts.  so my playtimes have been greatly reduced, so much so that you really don't see too many of the above (uber mob hits, kael arena raids) at 3 in the morning pacific time.  therefore, while i am familiar with many of the raid/group stuff that some of you have mentioned... it is, unfortunately, something that i just cannot do.<br>
<br>
